(84,6,'Introducing OpenAI Academy for News Organizations','OpenAI is launching the OpenAI Academy for News Organizations, a new learning hub built with the American Journalism Project and The Lenfest Institute to help newsrooms use AI effectively. The Academy offers training, practical use cases, and responsible-use guidance to support journalists, editors, and publishers as they adopt AI in their reporting and operations.','https://openai.com/index/openai-academy-for-news-organizations','','2025-12-17 06:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Introducing OpenAI Academy for News Organizations]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[OpenAI is launching the OpenAI Academy for News Organizations, a new learning hub built with the American Journalism Project and The Lenfest Institute to help newsrooms use AI effectively. The Academy offers training, practical use cases, and responsible-use guidance to support journalists, editors, and publishers as they adopt AI in their reporting and operations.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/openai-academy-for-news-organizations<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/openai-academy-for-news-organizations<\\/guid>\\n            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2025 06:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',40.21,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:35','2026-01-31 10:47:35'),
