(289,6,'AI in Australia—OpenAI’s Economic Blueprint','Today, OpenAI, in partnership with Mandala Partners, is sharing the OpenAI AI Economic Blueprint for Australia. At a time when boosting productivity has emerged as a national priority for Australia, the Blueprint provides a clear, actionable plan for how Australia can unlock the full economic and social potential of artificial intelligence.','https://openai.com/global-affairs/openais-australia-economic-blueprint','','2025-06-30 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[AI in Australia\\u2014OpenAI\\u2019s Economic Blueprint]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[Today, OpenAI, in partnership with Mandala Partners, is sharing the OpenAI AI Economic Blueprint for Australia. At a time when boosting productivity has emerged as a national priority for Australia, the Blueprint provides a clear, actionable plan for how Australia can unlock the full economic and social potential of artificial intelligence.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/global-affairs\\/openais-australia-economic-blueprint<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/global-affairs\\/openais-australia-economic-blueprint<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Company]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Mon, 30 Jun 2025 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',35.60,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:36','2026-01-31 10:47:36'),
(290,6,'Customizable, no-code voice agent automation with GPT-4o','Retell AI is transforming the call center with AI voice automation powered by GPT-4o and GPT-4.1. Its no-code platform enables businesses to launch natural, real-time voice agents that cut call costs, boost CSAT, and automate customer conversations—without scripts or hold times.','https://openai.com/index/retell-ai','','2025-06-26 10:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Customizable, no-code voice agent automation with GPT-4o]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[Retell AI is transforming the call center with AI voice automation powered by GPT-4o and GPT-4.1. Its no-code platform enables businesses to launch natural, real-time voice agents that cut call costs, boost CSAT, and automate customer conversations\\u2014without scripts or hold times.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/retell-ai<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/retell-ai<\\/guid>\\n            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 10:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',33.52,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:36','2026-01-31 10:47:36'),
