(320,6,'Sycophancy in GPT-4o: what happened and what we’re doing about it','We have rolled back last week’s GPT‑4o update in ChatGPT so people are now using an earlier version with more balanced behavior. The update we removed was overly flattering or agreeable—often described as sycophantic.','https://openai.com/index/sycophancy-in-gpt-4o','','2025-04-29 18:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Sycophancy in GPT-4o: what happened and what we\\u2019re doing about it]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We have rolled back last week\\u2019s GPT\\u20114o update in ChatGPT so people are now using an earlier version with more balanced behavior. The update we removed was overly flattering or agreeable\\u2014often described as sycophantic.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/sycophancy-in-gpt-4o<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/sycophancy-in-gpt-4o<\\/guid>\\n            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 18:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',31.64,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:36','2026-01-31 10:47:36'),
