(627,6,'GPT-4','We’ve created GPT-4, the latest milestone in OpenAI’s effort in scaling up deep learning. GPT-4 is a large multimodal model (accepting image and text inputs, emitting text outputs) that, while less capable than humans in many real-world scenarios, exhibits human-level performance on various professional and academic benchmarks.','https://openai.com/index/gpt-4-research','','2023-03-14 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[GPT-4]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We\\u2019ve created GPT-4, the latest milestone in OpenAI\\u2019s effort in scaling up deep learning. GPT-4 is a large multimodal model (accepting image and text inputs, emitting text outputs) that, while less capable than humans in many real-world scenarios, exhibits human-level performance on various professional and academic benchmarks.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/gpt-4-research<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/gpt-4-research<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Mar 2023 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',33.56,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
