(668,6,'Measuring Goodhart’s law','Goodhart’s law famously says: “When a measure becomes a target, it ceases to be a good measure.” Although originally from economics, it’s something we have to grapple with at OpenAI when figuring out how to optimize objectives that are difficult or costly to measure.','https://openai.com/index/measuring-goodharts-law','','2022-04-13 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Measuring Goodhart\\u2019s law]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[Goodhart\\u2019s law\\u00a0famously says: \\u201cWhen a measure becomes a target, it ceases to be a good measure.\\u201d Although originally from economics, it\\u2019s something we have to grapple with at OpenAI when figuring out how to optimize objectives that are difficult or costly to measure.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/measuring-goodharts-law<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/measuring-goodharts-law<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Safety & Alignment]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Apr 2022 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',32.12,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
