(681,6,'Solving math word problems','We’ve trained a system that solves grade school math problems with nearly twice the accuracy of a fine-tuned GPT-3 model. It solves about 90% as many problems as real kids: a small sample of 9-12 year olds scored 60% on a test from our dataset, while our system scored 55% on those same problems.','https://openai.com/index/solving-math-word-problems','','2021-10-29 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Solving math word problems]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We\\u2019ve trained\\u00a0a system that solves grade school math problems with nearly twice the accuracy of a fine-tuned GPT-3 model. It solves about 90% as many problems as real kids: a small sample of 9-12 year olds scored 60% on a test from our dataset, while our system scored 55% on those same problems.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/solving-math-word-problems<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/solving-math-word-problems<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Oct 2021 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',33.04,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
