(690,6,'Will Hurd joins OpenAI’s board of directors','OpenAI is committed to developing general-purpose artificial intelligence that benefits all humanity, and we believe that achieving our goal requires expertise in public policy as well as technology. So, we’re delighted to announce that Congressman Will Hurd has joined our board of directors.','https://openai.com/index/will-hurd-joins','','2021-05-03 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Will Hurd joins OpenAI\\u2019s board of directors]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[OpenAI is committed to developing general-purpose artificial intelligence that benefits all humanity, and we believe that achieving our goal requires expertise in public policy as well as technology. So, we\\u2019re delighted to announce that Congressman\\u00a0Will Hurd\\u00a0has joined our board of directors.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/will-hurd-joins<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/will-hurd-joins<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Company]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Mon, 03 May 2021 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',37.25,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
