(703,6,'Image GPT','We find that, just as a large transformer model trained on language can generate coherent text, the same exact model trained on pixel sequences can generate coherent image completions and samples. By establishing a correlation between sample quality and image classification accuracy, we show that our best generative model also contains features competitive with top convolutional nets in the unsupervised setting.','https://openai.com/index/image-gpt','','2020-06-17 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Image GPT]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We find that, just as a large transformer model trained on language can generate coherent text, the same exact model trained on pixel sequences can generate coherent image\\u00a0completions\\u00a0and\\u00a0samples. By establishing a correlation between sample quality and image classification accuracy, we show that our best generative model also contains features competitive with top convolutional nets in the unsupervised\\u00a0setting.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/image-gpt<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/image-gpt<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2020 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',37.16,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
