(758,6,'OpenAI Five Benchmark: Results','Yesterday, OpenAI Five won a best-of-three against a team of 99.95th percentile Dota players: Blitz, Cap, Fogged, Merlini, and MoonMeander—four of whom have played Dota professionally—in front of a live audience and 100,000 concurrent livestream viewers.','https://openai.com/index/openai-five-benchmark-results','','2018-08-06 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[OpenAI Five Benchmark: Results]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[Yesterday,\\u00a0OpenAI Five\\u00a0won a best-of-three against a team of 99.95th percentile Dota players:\\u00a0Blitz,\\u00a0Cap,\\u00a0Fogged,\\u00a0Merlini, and\\u00a0MoonMeander\\u2014four of whom have played Dota professionally\\u2014in front of a live audience and 100,000 concurrent livestream\\u00a0viewers.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/openai-five-benchmark-results<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/openai-five-benchmark-results<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Aug 2018 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',31.88,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
