(768,6,'Improving language understanding with unsupervised learning','We’ve obtained state-of-the-art results on a suite of diverse language tasks with a scalable, task-agnostic system, which we’re also releasing. Our approach is a combination of two existing ideas: transformers and unsupervised pre-training. These results provide a convincing example that pairing supervised learning methods with unsupervised pre-training works very well; this is an idea that many have explored in the past, and we hope our result motivates further research into applying this idea on larger and more diverse datasets.','https://openai.com/index/language-unsupervised','','2018-06-11 07:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Improving language understanding with unsupervised learning]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We\\u2019ve obtained state-of-the-art results on a suite of diverse language tasks with a scalable, task-agnostic system, which we\\u2019re also releasing. Our approach is a combination of two existing ideas:\\u00a0transformers\\u00a0and\\u00a0unsupervised pre-training. These results provide a convincing example that pairing supervised learning methods with unsupervised pre-training works very well; this is an idea that many have explored in the past, and we hope our result motivates further research into applying this idea on larger and more diverse\\u00a0datasets.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/language-unsupervised<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/language-unsupervised<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Safety & Alignment]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Mon, 11 Jun 2018 07:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',43.53,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
