(785,6,'Ingredients for robotics research','We’re releasing eight simulated robotics environments and a Baselines implementation of Hindsight Experience Replay, all developed for our research over the past year. We’ve used these environments to train models which work on physical robots. We’re also releasing a set of requests for robotics research.','https://openai.com/index/ingredients-for-robotics-research','','2018-02-26 08:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Ingredients for robotics research]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We\\u2019re releasing eight simulated robotics environments and a Baselines implementation of Hindsight Experience Replay, all developed for our research over the past year. We\\u2019ve used these environments to train models which work on physical robots. We\\u2019re also releasing a set of requests for robotics research.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/ingredients-for-robotics-research<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/ingredients-for-robotics-research<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2018 08:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',33.84,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
