(793,6,'Block-sparse GPU kernels','We’re releasing highly-optimized GPU kernels for an underexplored class of neural network architectures: networks with block-sparse weights. Depending on the chosen sparsity, these kernels can run orders of magnitude faster than cuBLAS or cuSPARSE. We’ve used them to attain state-of-the-art results in text sentiment analysis and generative modeling of text and images.','https://openai.com/index/block-sparse-gpu-kernels','','2017-12-06 08:00:00','{\"raw_item\":\"<item>\\n            <title><![CDATA[Block-sparse GPU kernels]]><\\/title>\\n            <description><![CDATA[We\\u2019re releasing highly-optimized GPU kernels for an underexplored class of neural network architectures: networks with block-sparse weights. Depending on the chosen sparsity, these kernels can run orders of magnitude faster than cuBLAS or cuSPARSE. We\\u2019ve used them to attain state-of-the-art results in text sentiment analysis and generative modeling of text and images.]]><\\/description>\\n            <link>https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/block-sparse-gpu-kernels<\\/link>\\n            <guid isPermaLink=\\\"true\\\">https:\\/\\/openai.com\\/index\\/block-sparse-gpu-kernels<\\/guid>\\n            <category><![CDATA[Research]]><\\/category>\\n            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2017 08:00:00 GMT<\\/pubDate>\\n        <\\/item>\",\"source_name\":\"OpenAI Blog\"}',35.96,NULL,0.00,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'pending',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-31 10:47:37','2026-01-31 10:47:37'),
